  li Can Assistive Technologies read text alternatives aloud, present then visually, or convert to braille for people who have difficulty perceiving visual content, or have difficulty understanding the meaning of prerecorded video content?
  li Can text be read for people who are deaf, are hard of hearing, or who are having trouble understanding audio information for any reason?
